reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:118:      "Jodo Shinshu teachers for Other Power contrast",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:127:      "Huangbo, On the Transmission of Mind, Blofeld translation hosted at https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a1-chun-chou-record.htm and https://selfdefinition.org/zen/huang-po/transmission/a2-chun-chou-record-cont.htm, read with Dogen Bendowa excerpts at https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and Soto shusho itto note at https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:129:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model can make search-refusal too clean. Huangbo taught through dialogue, Dogen built a practice institution, and Dzogchen no-path language often requires teacher transmission. The modern cohort is clear but narrow: stable over-managers and perfectionistic practitioners who audit their inner state. It is not for beginners needing inquiry, people using non-inquiry to avoid repair, OCD or scrupulosity, dissociation, severe depression, mania, psychosis, acute trauma, addiction withdrawal, or medical blackout concerns.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:130:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Search further in Collingwood on the logic of question and answer, Gadamer on the priority of the question, Asad on discursive tradition, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Austin on felicity conditions, Sharf and Katz on contextualism, Dogen scholarship on shusho itto, Chan studies on Huangbo and Bankei, Dzogchen direct-introduction literature, VCE and Cheetah House safety literature, and spiritual bypassing research.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:131:    "structural_observation": "SN 22.59 and SN 22.95 explicitly authorize seeing, observing, examining, disenchantment, release, and the knowledge that the task is done. That is a staged investigative grammar. Huangbo repeatedly treats seeking Mind with mind, forming concepts of the Way, or making the Way into a road as the very distortion. Dogen's practice-realization unity blocks a simple cause-then-result reading, while Soto material also says Dogen emphasized active practice because realization is already present. The candidate's gate is textually plausible, but only if it codes the native practice grammar rather than broad tradition names."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-paths-refuse-the-question-of-what-remains-d756c9bf775096c6.json:143:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Huangbo, Dogen, Collingwood, Gadamer, VCE, and prior Lumenary no-management records, this idea's specific contribution is a precondition test before remainder coding: only ask what remains if the path first authorizes a self-negation event with an after."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.md:27:- MN 22 raft simile, Heart Sutra no attainment, and Dogen practice-realization, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html, https://www.lotsawahouse.org/words-of-the-buddha/heart-sutra, https://buddhismnow.com/2023/10/08/practice-within-realisation-dogen/
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.md:29:Structural observation: Zhuangzi and MN 22 both support release of a tool after its work is done, but they presuppose a real catch or crossing. MN 22 also stresses proper grasp before release, which prevents premature quitting. The Heart Sutra denies attainment while still relying on Prajnaparamita, so no-attainment is not simple inactivity. Dogen strains the model most, because practice and realization are inseparable, which blocks a universal before-and-after completion rule. These primary texts support a scoped after-use discipline, not the broad claim that finishing is always the next virtue.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.md:33:Risk of overread: High. Spiritual release texts can be misused to justify quitting hard work, while Dogen can be misused to justify endless practice with no deliverable. The engine evidence is procedural, not doctrinal: it repeatedly ignored a logged audit or merge step.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-can-native-verification-or-authority-boundaries-be-identified-non-circularly-acro.md:9:Both agents agree that the original typology was too stable and that translation strain requires decomposition by stage, genre, metaphysical register, institutional form, and practice context. They also converge on Dogen's practice-realization identity as a genuine fourth configuration and on the need to test whether reflexive operations predict verification and transmission after controls.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If Eihei Shingi, Soto training, Shinran's cautions against licensed evil, nembutsu practice, and community transmission all function as retained disciplines with real effects, then non-instrumentality is not outside the custody apparatus. It is a different custody location: form-held, vow-held, teacher-held, conduct-held, or community-held."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:12:    "Dogen's practice-realization makes sitting not a bridge to later enlightenment but the expression of realization itself.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:13:    "Shinran's Other Power denies practicer calculation and owned efficacy.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:25:  "exact_claim": "Before asking what a practice does with authority over its result, ask whether it claims to produce a separable result at all. Custody, release, and correction vocabulary applies only to instrumental practices. Dogen's practice-realization and Shinran's Other Power dissolve the tool frame because sitting or entrusting is not owned as a means to a later product.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:31:      "test_surface": "Split-source coding of Dogen, Shinran, MN 22, koan curricula, Advaita inquiry, apophatic Christian sources, Sufi fana and baqa, and ritual manuals.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:50:    "Dogen shusho itto practice realization one cause effect practice realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:51:    "Shinran jinen honi no calculation Other Power practicer",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:52:    "Tannisho nembutsu not practice not good act Other Power self power",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:64:      "overlap": "Extremely close. The prior audit already says keep, release, embody assumes practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and that Shinran and Dogen break those assumptions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:75:      "novelty_impact": "Downgrades the Dogen example to known Soto doctrine.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:77:      "source": "Dogen shusho itto, Soto Zen key term, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:80:      "difference": "The candidate uses Shinran as a non-tool boundary case rather than as Pure Land doctrine alone.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:82:      "overlap": "Very close. Shinran explicitly rejects practicer calculation and describes Other Power as no working, which undermines self-owned method efficacy.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:83:      "source": "Shinran, On Jinen Honi, https://shinranworks.com/hymns-in-japanese/hymns-of-the-dharma-ages/on-jinen-honi/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:99:      "novelty_impact": "For Shinran-style agency relocation, novelty is low unless the separable-result gate predicts warnings beyond agency-style variables.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:108:    "Read non-instrumental ritual theory, autotelic flow literature, MacIntyre on practices, Dogen's Eihei Shingi, Bendowa and Genjokoan, Shinran and Tannisho in stronger translations before public use.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:111:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.34. The instrumental versus non-instrumental distinction is old and appears directly in Dogen, Shinran, ritual theory, autotelic activity theory, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits. The useful extension is narrower: using separable-result as a pre-coding scope gate for Lumenary's custody and release apparatus. Human-condition fit is strong for functioning perfectionists, founders, students, creators, and professionals who convert every activity into proof of worth. It is not for under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, severe depression, dissociation, mania, psychosis, addiction withdrawal, acute crisis, coercive workloads, or people who need concrete completed outcomes restored before resultless practice is safe.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:114:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners and scholars say this is already standard as practice-realization, Other Power, autotelic ritual, internal goods, non-attachment, grace, or non-gaining mind, and that the scope gate adds no predictive guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:123:      "Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:136:      "Dogen shusho itto and Shinran jinen honi, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf and https://shinranworks.com/hymns-in-japanese/hymns-of-the-dharma-ages/on-jinen-honi/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:138:    "risk_of_overread": "High. Non-instrumental self-description does not mean absence of discipline, correction, warnings, institutional form, or effects. Dogen still requires continuous practice, and Shinran still has nembutsu, entrusting, and cautions. The model may confuse no owned result with no practical structure.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:139:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit did not read Eihei Shingi, full Bendowa or Genjokoan in Japanese, Shinran's Japanese around jinen and hakarai, Tannisho anti-license passages in Japanese, ritual theory in depth, Aristotle praxis and poiesis sources, or empirical studies of autotelic practice and perfectionism. These are necessary before raising novelty.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:140:    "structural_observation": "MN 22 is explicitly instrumental: effort with the raft gets one across, then the raft should not be carried. Dogen's shusho itto demolishes the cause-effect separation between practice and realization, while Shinran's jinen honi removes calculation by the practicer and locates efficacy in Other Power. The contrast supports a scope distinction, but not a discovery: the instrumental versus non-instrumental contrast is already structurally visible in the primary texts."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.json:152:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Dogen's practice-realization, Shinran's Other Power, autotelic activity theory, non-instrumental ritual theory, MacIntyre's internal goods, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits, this idea's possible contribution is a practical scope gate for comparative coding: ask first whether a practice claims to produce a separable result before applying custody, release, or correction vocabulary."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:44:- Dogen practice realization one Bendowa Advaita attainment already attained
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:50:- Steve Bein, Self Power, Other Power, and Non-Dualism in Japanese Buddhism, https://philpapers.org/rec/BEISPO: overlap: Close. Bein already treats self-power, other-power, and non-dualism as a philosophical variable inside Japanese Buddhism.; difference: The candidate generalizes beyond Japanese Buddhism and adds failure-mode and safeguard predictions.; novelty impact: High reduction, especially for the three core categories of practitioner, source, and nondual credit.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:54:- Dogen practice-realization, summarized in St Andrews Encyclopaedia of Theology, https://www.saet.ac.uk/Buddhism/Dogen: overlap: Close for activity-centered credit. Dogen's praxis is enlightenment, so practice is not merely a cause toward a later result.; difference: Dogen provides one type, not a comparative credit-distribution taxonomy.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for one category.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:73:- If: Credit distribution should be separable from the capacity ledger. Then: Two traditions can require similar receiving, agency, memory, reflexivity, and integration functions while crediting the power behind those functions differently, and this difference predicts different safeguards. Weakens if: Credit distribution always collapses into support locus, or support-locus coding predicts safeguards and failures without a separate credit variable. Test surface: Paired coding of Jodo Shinshu and Christian grace traditions, Soto Zen and Dzogchen, Theravada and Gita karma-yoga, with independent raters.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:74:- If: Stage transitions should be high-risk points when credit distribution changes. Then: Manuals and teachers mark special danger when a practitioner moves from effortful preparation to recognition, surrender, no-gaining practice, or already-accomplished realization. Weakens if: Transitions do not show distinctive warnings, or reported difficulties are better predicted by retreat intensity, trauma, doctrine learning, or social pressure. Test surface: Stage-coded readings of Theravada, Sufi, Advaita, Dzogchen, Soto, and Pure Land training sequences.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:113:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.74 to about 0.48. The five-type comparative frame is generative, but the main structure is anticipated by Pargament's religious coping styles, God-control attribution research, Christian monergism and synergism, Japanese self-power and other-power, Sri Vaishnava prapatti debates, Sufi station-state distinctions, Dogen practice-realization, and local Lumenary work.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.md:120:- Treat activity-centered and ground-centered categories as the only possible novelty zones, and search Dogen, Advaita, Dzogchen, and nondual scholarship for close prior forms.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.md:27:- Zhuangzi fish trap and words, https://ctext.org/zhuangzi/what-comes-from-without; Dogen Genjokoan practice-realization, https://brightwayzen.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/For-BWZ-Chant-Book-Genjokoan.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.md:29:Structural observation: MN 22 and Zhuangzi support releasing a tool after it has done its work, but both presuppose that the work really has been done. The Heart Sutra keeps reliance after denying attainment, so not every repeated form is clinging. Dogen sharply strains the claim because ongoing expression of realization can require repeated practice without a separate product. Primary texts therefore support a narrow anti-duplication rule only where a restatement adds no new source, anomaly, prediction, or conduct change.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:26:- Heart Sutra and Dogen shusho itto sources, https://www.mnzencenter.org/uploads/2/9/5/8/29581455/heart.pdf and https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:28:Structural observation: MN 22 is a direct release template: the Dhamma is used for crossing and then not carried. The Heart Sutra complicates release because it denies path and attainment while still relying on Prajnaparamita, mantra, recitation, and teacher-mediated practice. Dogen complicates both retention and abandonment because practice and realization are described as one, so there is no clean after-stage where custody is decided.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Before any public claim, read fuller work on upaya, raft and ladder metaphors, Wittgenstein's ladder, Nagarjuna's no-thesis claim, Hori on koan pedagogy, Sells on apophasis, Hadot on spiritual exercises, Dogen scholarship, Shinran scholarship, and Pargament on religious agency styles. Japanese, Pali, Sanskrit, and Chinese terms were not checked here.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:38:- Dogen Bendowa shusho itto practice realization one primary source
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:48:- Internal Lumenary audit, The Road Must Know Its End, reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json: overlap: Extremely close. The prior audit already names keep, release, and embody as an after-use rubric and lowers novelty for the same MN 22, Heart Sutra, Dogen, Sells, Smith, and achievement-pressure basis.; difference: This candidate states the two axes more explicitly and frames the issue as method shape rather than road completion.; novelty impact: Major downgrade. This is mostly a renamed or slightly sharpened version of the existing Lumenary after-use model.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:53:- Dogen shusho itto, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Close as anomaly and near-neighbor: practice-realization refuses a simple means-result-after sequence.; difference: The candidate treats this as an embodied or third post-use category, while Dogen may reject the post-use grid itself.; novelty impact: Forces downgrade and bounded use. If Dogen is not on the axis, the model must become a scope-limited heuristic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:57:Unlike MN 22, Wittgenstein's ladder, Smith's Nagarjuna-Wittgenstein therapy, Sells's apophatic unsaying, Dogen's practice-realization, and prior Lumenary after-use models, this idea's possible contribution is a bounded coding rubric that tests whether method type predicts held-out warnings, repairs, and post-insight temptations in achievement-pressured practitioners.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:61:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, Shinran Other Power, and the Heart Sutra's no-attainment-with-reliance pattern.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:69:- If: Method shape predicts aftermath instruction. Then: Blind coders can code validates versus undermines and retained versus abandoned versus embodied from instruction passages, then predict held-out warnings, repairs, and verification rules better than tradition label alone. Weakens if: Coders cannot agree on the axes, or the axes do not predict held-out warnings better than generic variables such as teacher style, institution, practice intensity, or tradition identity. Test surface: Split-source corpus coding across MN 22, Heart Sutra, Mandukya, Dogen, Shinran, apophatic Christian, Sufi, Advaita, and koan-training sources.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.md:78:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-self-was-never-a-conclusion-ebf3587c6da573ba.json:12:    "Shankara's witness or consciousness is svaprakasha and self-established, not inferred as a remainder.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-self-was-never-a-conclusion-ebf3587c6da573ba.json:77:      "source": "Internal Lumenary dialogue, 2026-05-26, disclosure-exempting remainder-testing revision, reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-whether-the-revised-taxonomy-disclosure-exempting-remainder-testing-rema.md"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen's practice-realization identity and Shinran's Other Power.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Dogen strains the premise that a road first leads to an end and then receives an after-use instruction. Shinran strains the premise that the practitioner owns the road, trust, or result enough to retain, release, or embody it. These cases may sit outside the grid's conditions of askability."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:12:    "Hybrid cases such as MN 22, the Heart Sutra, Rinzai koan curriculum, and Dogen's practice-realization expose the weakness of a simple confirm-or-cancel typology.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:30:      "test_surface": "Inter-rater coding of MN 22, Heart Sutra, Dogen Bendowa or Genjokoan, Tannisho, Rinzai koan curriculum sources, apophatic Christian texts, and Sufi fana or baqa sources.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:48:    "Dogen practice realization one shusho itto no verification outside practice",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:84:      "difference": "The candidate tries to absorb this as embodied after-use, but Dogen may reject the tool-result framing altogether.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:85:      "novelty_impact": "Major anomaly pressure. If Dogen cannot be coded reliably, the model is only a limited checklist.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:97:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.61 to 0.31. The two-axis structure is already an internal audit instruction, and the individual components are strongly represented in MN 22, upaya, apophasis, Dogen, and therapeutic-method literature. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: achievement-driven people who convert methods and insights into worth. Non-fit cases include acute crisis, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, dissociation, psychosis, under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, and structural burnout where the primary remedy is workload or institutional change rather than reflection.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:110:      "Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:123:    "risk_of_overread": "High. Retained, released, and embodied may be analyst categories that flatten native distinctions. Dogen-style practice-realization, Shinran's Other Power, and no-attainment Prajnaparamita may not be hard cases inside the grid; they may reject the temporal and ownership assumptions that make the grid possible.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:124:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit did not newly inspect Pali, Sanskrit, Chinese, or Japanese originals. Before publication, read fuller work on upaya, raft and ladder metaphors, Hori on koan curricula, Sells on unsaying, Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Dogen scholarship on practice-realization, Shinran scholarship on Other Power, Pargament on agency styles, and Hadot on spiritual exercises.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.json:137:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike MN 22, upaya, Sells, Smith, Dogen scholarship, and prior Lumenary custody models, this idea's possible contribution is a bounded two-variable after-use rubric that predicts when a practitioner should keep a method, set it down, or let it appear as conduct, especially for achievement-driven people who turn tools into proof of worth."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:25:- Shinran, Tannisho, A Record in Lament of Divergences, https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:27:Structural observation: SN 45.8 makes right effort operational and practitioner-facing: desire, endeavor, persistence, intent, and maintenance of skillful qualities are all assigned to the monk's practice field. Tannisho reverses the claimant grammar: nembutsu is not a practice or good act when it arises from Other Power, and claims such as my disciples are rejected because the working belongs to Amida. The comparison supports a real difference in claimant policy, but Tannisho is not a late handoff after training. It often refuses self-claim from the entrance, so the model needs a no-transfer or analyst-frame-refused value.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:29:Secondary literature gap: The search found close prior structures in religious coping styles, self-power and other-power, Dogen practice-realization, Dzogchen direct introduction, Engler on ego strength before no-self, the Buddhist raft and upaya pattern, and local Lumenary capacity-ledger and credit-distribution work. I did not find the exact field list as a cross-tradition coding sheet, but the core agency-allocation and means-end reversal are well established.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:36:- Steve Bein Self Power Other Power and Non-Dualism in Japanese Buddhism
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:37:- Shinran Tannisho chapter 1 nembutsu mind arises Amida working
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:39:- Dogen practice-realization not means to end shusho
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:47:- Steve Bein, Self Power, Other Power, and Non-Dualism in Japanese Buddhism, https://philpapers.org/rec/BEISPO: overlap: Very close for treating self-power, other-power, and non-dualism as structured alternatives rather than a simple binary.; difference: The candidate generalizes beyond Japanese Buddhism and asks where the transfer occurs for each trained function.; novelty impact: High reduction for the effort-gift architecture, moderate reduction for stage-sensitive coding.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:48:- Shinran, Tannisho chapters 1, 6, 8, and 11, https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/: overlap: Near exact for forbidden claimant language. The nembutsu is said to arise from Other Power, and even disciple ownership is rejected.; difference: Tannisho is a primary instance, not a comparative rubric. It may actually break the model by refusing the idea that a human function is first trained and then handed off.; novelty impact: High reduction and a major anomaly.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:50:- Dogen practice-realization, St Andrews Encyclopaedia of Theology, https://www.saet.ac.uk/Buddhism/Dogen and Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy, https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/japanese-zen/: overlap: Close for collapsing practice and realization, removing practice as a bridge to later gain.; difference: Dogen is one type within the proposed rubric, not the whole comparative model.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for the practice-realization category.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:57:Unlike Pargament, self-power and other-power debates, Dogen practice-realization, and local Lumenary credit models, this idea says the decisive unit is a timed transfer for each required function, with observable safeguards and repairs at that transfer point.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:63:Why it strains the model: If even hearing, saying, entrusting, and gratitude are Amida's working rather than trained human functions, then the analyst's transfer language may smuggle self-power into a tradition built to reject that framing. Dogen also strains the model because practice-realization collapses bridge and arrival rather than transferring ownership from one holder to another.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:69:- If: Manuals should mark transfer points with special safeguards rather than generic warnings. Then: Pure Land texts should warn against calculation, Dzogchen texts against contrivance and premature recognition, Soto texts against gaining idea, early Buddhist texts against appropriation of aggregates or attainment ownership, and Gita-style karma-yoga texts against fruit ownership. Weakens if: Warnings cluster by institution, teacher temperament, ethics, or historical polemic rather than by transfer point. Test surface: Blind stage-coded manual analysis across at least three texts per tradition.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:71:- If: The handoff rubric should add predictive value beyond Pargament-style responsibility allocation and the local capacity ledger. Then: Two practices with the same broad credit type but different transfer timing show different safeguards and repair instructions. Weakens if: Support locus and credit-distribution coding predict the same outcomes without needing handoff timing. Test surface: Inter-rater coding of matched pairs such as Soto and Dzogchen, Pure Land and Christian grace, Theravada and karma-yoga.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:79:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:111:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.53 to about 0.44. The rubric is generative, but its parts are heavily anticipated by religious coping styles, self-power and other-power discourse, Dogen, Dzogchen manuals, the raft and upaya pattern, Engler, and local Lumenary priors. Treat as a consolidation unless inter-rater coding shows new predictive value.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-handoff-point-is-the-variable-2942cf211db9ae34.md:117:- Code primary manuals before broad tradition labels, beginning with SN 45.8, Tannisho chapters 1, 6, 8, and 11, Longchen Rabjam Trekcho, Bendowa or Dogen practice-realization sources, and one Christian grace manual.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:12:After de-identification or objectless-awareness practice, the decisive comparative unit is not simply the remainder after negation, but the authorization mode by which a passage, teacher, model, or practitioner is permitted to rest, investigate, deny, bracket, teach, or refuse a post-negation seeming. This authorization must be coded by textual stratum and claim level, and the rubric is only useful if it can fail and if practitioner-facing counsel reduces distress without increasing inflation, dissociation, nihilistic deflation, or rumination.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:53:- Nagarjuna, Mulamadhyamakakarika 18.6 and related Madhyamaka non-thesis readings: overlap: Close on refusing to convert analysis into a positive remainder claim, and on treating silence or non-position as a disciplined outcome rather than ignorance.; difference: Madhyamaka is a specific philosophical practice, while the candidate compares multiple authorization modes across traditions and neuroscience.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction and important anomaly pressure. Some mature sources authorize refusal without a remainder or recognition verdict.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:63:Candidate: Madhyamaka and direct-recognition cases where the mature instruction refuses both a positive remainder and a neutral bracket, or where a qualified teacher authorizes recognition without the analyst being able to separate recognition, assertion, and pedagogical performance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:65:Why it strains the model: If a text or practice intentionally collapses the distinction between denial, refusal, and recognition, the authorization-mode grid may impose categories the source rejects. Dogen practice-realization, Dzogchen pointing-out, Mahamudra direct introduction, and some Madhyamaka sources may make authorization inseparable from performance and relation, not a codeable stance after an event.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:71:- If: Post-negation authorization mode is a real comparative variable rather than a relabeling of tradition identity. Then: Blind coders using source-stratum passages can predict held-out warnings, repair instructions, or teacher counsel better than coders using tradition label, generic doctrine, or neuroscience mechanism alone. Weakens if: Inter-rater agreement is poor, all major passages require multiple equally plausible modes, or tradition label predicts warnings and repairs as well as the authorization rubric. Test surface: Split-source coding study across Brihadaranyaka, Shankara, SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Udana 1.10, MMK 18.6, Dogen, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, and contemporary mindfulness adverse-event guidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization-940b94daf10fd12f.md:82:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:12:No-distance teachings may remove the private project of becoming spiritual, but they do not thereby remove care, correction, companionship, schedule, teacher, text, vow, or ordinary accountability. Before asking what remains after self-negation, code whether the path grants the practitioner ownership at all. If ownership is refused, the key question is where correction is held and whether failures cluster when students privatize the insight, abandon correction, become passive, or turn relief into performance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:17:- Anti-ownership should be coded before remainder, residue, or completion variables.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:26:- Dogen Bendowa and Soto shusho itto sources, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf, read against Huangbo, The Transmission of Mind, Blofeld record https://merton.bellarmine.edu/s/merton/media/51897 and searchable PDF used at https://wayofsuddenawakening.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Huang-Po-The-Transmission-of-Mind.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:27:- Shinran, Tannisho, especially preface, chapters 1, 6, 8, 10, 11, and 12, https://jodoshinshu.faith/tannisho-a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:29:Structural observation: Dogen's practice-realization unity rejects practice as a cause separate from later realization, but Soto explanatory material also says Dogen emphasized active practice because realization is already present. Huangbo is a sharper anomaly: he rejects objective seeking and objective path language, yet the record is itself teacher discourse and includes testing a teacher's groundedness and warning against casual pilgrimage. Tannisho denies self-powered practice and calculation, yet it opens by lamenting divergences, relies on true teachers, and preserves Vow, teacher, and correction. The candidate's narrow claim survives as a hypothesis: no-distance language is not automatically support-free, but the specific holder must be coded natively.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:31:Secondary literature gap: Read full Dogen Bendowa, Genjokoan, Uji, Eihei Shingi, and Soto scholarship; Huangbo in multiple translations plus Chan transmission studies; Shinran, Tannisho, jinen, hakarai, and Other Power scholarship; Dzogchen and Mahamudra direct introduction manuals; Asad, Lindbeck, MacIntyre, Bell, Sharf, Katz, spiritual bypassing research, VCE, Cheetah House, mindfulness optimization critique, and spiritual direction ethics. Interviews with no-distance practitioners are essential.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:33:Risk of overread: High. The model can become circular by counting any surviving text, teacher, or community as support. It can also domesticate Huangbo-style search-refusal by turning an anti-support discourse into analyst-defined support. It may hide abuse if correction holders are assumed safe, and it may pathologize valid solitude. Human-condition fit is clear but narrow: stable isolated over-managers, app meditators, retreatants, and self-improvers. It is not a loneliness cure by itself and can increase dependency, rumination, or unsafe authority compliance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:37:- Dogen Bendowa practice realization shusho itto no gaining practice realization one
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:38:- Huangbo Transmission of Mind no seeking objective path teacher support correction
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:39:- Shinran Tannisho Other Power self power divergence true teacher correction
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:46:- Dzogchen direct introduction support teacher correction no path practice
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:56:- Soto Zen shusho itto source, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: It already states that practice and realization are inseparable while Dogen strongly emphasizes active practice, so no-gap is not no-practice.; difference: The candidate generalizes this into a comparative rule across no-distance teachings and support ecologies.; novelty impact: Major reduction for Dogen-specific originality, partial preservation for cross-case testing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:57:- Huangbo, Transmission of Mind, Blofeld record https://merton.bellarmine.edu/s/merton/media/51897 and searchable PDF https://wayofsuddenawakening.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Huang-Po-The-Transmission-of-Mind.pdf: overlap: Huangbo already supplies the no-seeking pressure and warnings about false teachers, casual pilgrimage, and conceptual path-making.; difference: The candidate may overuse Huangbo as support for correction when his discourse also cuts support-seeking itself.; novelty impact: Acts more as anomaly than support. It lowers confidence unless coded natively.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:61:Unlike Keep What Can Correct You, Some Help Should Not Be Managed, Asad, Lindbeck, VCE, spiritual bypassing research, and Soto practice-realization sources, this idea's specific contribution is to make anti-ownership a pre-remainder coding gate for no-distance teachings and to predict that loss of correction support will produce privatization, passivity, or performance failures.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:73:- If: No-distance teachings refuse private ownership but preserve some concrete correction or care holder. Then: Split-source coding of Dogen, Huangbo, Shinran, Dzogchen, and Mahamudra sources will find ownership refusal in one layer and held-out warnings, teacher checks, vow, practice form, text, community, conduct, or reentry rules in another. Weakens if: Sources deny both private ownership and codeable correction holders, or coders cannot distinguish support from the mere existence of a tradition. Test surface: Pre-registered primary-text codebook with source layer, ownership, after, correction holder, support holder, warning, repair, and analyst-frame refusal.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:76:- If: Anti-ownership support coding adds decision power beyond prior Lumenary records. Then: Blind coders can use anti-ownership and correction-holder fields to predict held-out warnings and repairs in no-distance cases better than Keep What Can Correct You, Some Help Should Not Be Managed, tradition label, or generic VCE factors alone. Weakens if: The new fields do not change decisions, or blind readers cannot state the difference from existing correction-holder and no-management records. Test surface: A/B coding comparison on Dogen, Huangbo, Tannisho, Dzogchen, Mahamudra, Pure Land, and one causal Theravada path.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:82:- Chan or Zen teachers familiar with Huangbo
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:84:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:97:- Would the pre-remainder ownership gate change screening, sequencing, warning, or repair instructions in your setting?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:99:Answers that reduce originality: Originality falls if practitioners say the rule is standard lineage pedagogy, spiritual direction, sangha correction, Soto practice-realization, Shin Other Power instruction, or meditation-safety triage, and if the support check adds no decisions beyond existing practice guidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:101:Answers that support contribution: Support rises if practitioners find that coding ownership refusal before remainder prevents real interpretive errors, predicts failure cases, and improves support routing without increasing self-effort, dependency, or unsafe authority.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:124:- Build a pre-remainder codebook with fields for ownership grant, no-distance grammar, permitted after, correction holder, support holder, warning, repair, unsafe holder, valid solitude, clinical exclusion, and analyst-frame refusal.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care-5e945a54e9681489.md:126:- Test Dogen, Huangbo, Tannisho, Dzogchen or Mahamudra direct introduction, Pure Land, and one causal Theravada path before broad tradition claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:26:- Dogen, Genjokoan, Aitken and Tanahashi translation, https://www.jasonong.com/5499, read against James and Ignatius as a practice-realization pressure case
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:28:Structural observation: James already separates origin from value and gives a fruits-over-roots test for religious life. Ignatius operationalizes a practitioner version: movements are discerned by where they lead, by timing, by desolation safeguards, and by disclosure to a competent spiritual person. Dogen adds a different enacted-test structure: realization is not certified before practice, it occurs in doing and returning to the place of practice. These sources strongly anticipate the contact-and-conduct side. The candidate's distinct move is not conduct-testing itself, but routing: source-first for public claim, contact-first for stable private orientation, then delayed provenance before teaching or identity authority.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:57:- Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.jasonong.com/5499 and secondary discussion of Dogen's realization-based language, https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/12/2/81: overlap: Close on enacted verification and resistance to pre-certifying realization before practice.; difference: Dogen's structure is native to transmitted Zen practice, not an open rule for borrowing sentences from other traditions.; novelty impact: Supports the analogy but lowers novelty of carry-first practice logic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:67:Unlike Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, James, Ignatius, Dogen, Wuthnow, Turkle, social prescribing, anti-checking psychology, and recent Lumenary translation-strain records, this candidate's specific contribution is a two-track routing rule: borrowed language used as public doctrine or evidence must pass provenance and regeneration first, while borrowed language used privately by a stable lonely seeker should first be carried into safe contact and conduct so it does not become a substitute for belonging, repair, grief work, or help-seeking.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:125:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.50 to 0.46. The doctrine half is close to Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, and prior Lumenary translation-strain gates. The seeker half is close to Jamesian fruits, Ignatian discernment, Dogen practice-realization, Wuthnow's seeker spirituality, Turkle's conversation critique, social prescribing, behavioral activation, and anti-checking psychology. The contribution is a compact routing rule by function and wound. Human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: stable lonely or digitally unmoored seekers with meaning loss, feeling out of place, digital comparison, or achievement-contingent spiritual identity. Practice-testability drops sharply without a pre-contact safety screen and delayed provenance review.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:18:- Hybrid cases such as MN 22, the Heart Sutra, Rinzai koan curriculum, and Dogen's practice-realization expose the weakness of a simple confirm-or-cancel typology.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:30:Secondary literature gap: This audit did not newly inspect Pali, Sanskrit, Chinese, or Japanese originals. Before publication, read fuller work on upaya, raft and ladder metaphors, Hori on koan curricula, Sells on unsaying, Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Dogen scholarship on practice-realization, Shinran scholarship on Other Power, Pargament on agency styles, and Hadot on spiritual exercises.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:32:Risk of overread: High. Retained, released, and embodied may be analyst categories that flatten native distinctions. Dogen-style practice-realization, Shinran's Other Power, and no-attainment Prajnaparamita may not be hard cases inside the grid; they may reject the temporal and ownership assumptions that make the grid possible.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:41:- Dogen practice realization one shusho itto no verification outside practice
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:52:- Soto Zen, Practice and Realization Are One, https://www.sotozen.com/eng/library/stories/vol01.html: overlap: Close anomaly to any road-then-end sequence, since practice itself is presented as realization rather than a means to later attainment.; difference: The candidate tries to absorb this as embodied after-use, but Dogen may reject the tool-result framing altogether.; novelty impact: Major anomaly pressure. If Dogen cannot be coded reliably, the model is only a limited checklist.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:56:Unlike MN 22, upaya, Sells, Smith, Dogen scholarship, and prior Lumenary custody models, this idea's possible contribution is a bounded two-variable after-use rubric that predicts when a practitioner should keep a method, set it down, or let it appear as conduct, especially for achievement-driven people who turn tools into proof of worth.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:60:Candidate: Dogen's practice-realization identity and Shinran's Other Power.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:62:Why it strains the model: Dogen strains the premise that a road first leads to an end and then receives an after-use instruction. Shinran strains the premise that the practitioner owns the road, trust, or result enough to retain, release, or embody it. These cases may sit outside the grid's conditions of askability.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:68:- If: Mature practice traditions vary systematically in after-use guidance. Then: Split-source coding will find distinct markers for retain, release, embody, no-threshold, practice-realization, and no-owner cases, and those markers will predict held-out warnings, verification rules, and repair practices. Weakens if: Coders cannot agree on the categories, or tradition identity, teacher style, institution type, and general agency models predict warnings just as well. Test surface: Inter-rater coding of MN 22, Heart Sutra, Dogen Bendowa or Genjokoan, Tannisho, Rinzai koan curriculum sources, apophatic Christian texts, and Sufi fana or baqa sources.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:75:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-the-road-must-know-its-end-ddc62528ba3f429d.md:108:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.61 to 0.31. The two-axis structure is already an internal audit instruction, and the individual components are strongly represented in MN 22, upaya, apophasis, Dogen, and therapeutic-method literature. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: achievement-driven people who convert methods and insights into worth. Non-fit cases include acute crisis, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, dissociation, psychosis, under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, and structural burnout where the primary remedy is workload or institutional change rather than reflection.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-whether-the-separability-thesis-survives-the-method-dependency-concession-if-con.md:9:Both agents converged on a two-stage comparison: method structure conditions whether remainder pressure arises at all; inference policy conditions how the pressure is interpreted when it does arise. They also converged on the testability of the crux through micro-phenomenological interviews with cross-trained practitioners, and agreed that cessation is a genuine boundary case rather than an exception to be accommodated.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-whether-the-separability-thesis-survives-the-method-dependency-concession-if-con.md:13:Whether the separability thesis survives the method-dependency concession. If contemplative training shapes not only how practitioners interpret the pressure but whether the pressure arises at all, then occurrence and interpretation are entangled from the start. The clean analytic cut between them may be a useful methodological fiction rather than a phenomenological discovery. Cross-trained practitioners could test the empirical question (does the same person report pressure during Advaita inquiry and not during Dzogchen practice?), but even positive results would show learned repertoire rather than settle whether the pressure has a single phenomenological character across training contexts.
findings/convergences/2026-05-26-whether-the-separability-thesis-survives-the-method-dependency-concession-if-con.md:17:Can the occurrence of a contemplative phenomenological state (such as remainder pressure, witness-awareness, or cessation) be analytically separated from the training context that conditions the practitioner to recognize and report it, or does the training context partly constitute the state itself? If constitutive, what are the consequences for any cross-traditional comparison that assumes a shared phenomenological substrate beneath different doctrinal interpretations?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-what-holds-you-that-you-did-not-build-e30798c2dedf5eaa.json:25:  "exact_claim": "For people whose steadiness and worth were held mostly by performance and self-command, collapse should be more total than for people whose continuity already lived partly in body, relationship, routine, duty, faith, or recovery support. The broad comparative claim about continuity after self-negation is old and overbuilt. The defensible contribution is a narrow person-level prediction plus a boundary condition: no-gap paths such as Dogen-style practice-realization should not be forced into a carry-across-a-threshold model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-what-holds-you-that-you-did-not-build-e30798c2dedf5eaa.json:41:      "expected_observation": "Dogen, Huangbo, and Dzogchen direct-recognition sources should not describe continuity as something carried across a before-after threshold; they should emphasize present practice, direct recognition, or search refusal instead.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-what-holds-you-that-you-did-not-build-e30798c2dedf5eaa.json:43:      "test_surface": "Split-source close reading of Bendowa, Genjokoan or Uji, Huangbo transmission texts, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and practitioner interviews.",
