reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:171:      "Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with Other Power and shinjin",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-credit-constrained-residue-authorization-as-a-two-variable-model-of-post-negation-translation-strain-a66d453d1d56cbe8.json:185:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model can make credit distribution look upstream by definition. Apophatic silence may arise from a theory of predication rather than appropriation risk. Dzogchen and Zen may block the search sequence before residue appears. Pure Land may reject the whole self-owned capacity frame. If the same passages are used to code credit and residue, the model becomes circular.",
